Save.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra] The title of save button on property pane.

Close.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra] The accessible label of button for closing property pane.

SaveConfirmation.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra] Confirmation message for the screen reader.
SaveConfirmation.value: We saved your changes in the property pane.

PropertyPaneBackPage.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra] The title of the back button on the property pane.

PropertyPaneNextPage.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra] The title of the next button on the property pane.

PropertyPanePageOfPages.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra] Placeholder={0} is current page number, placeholder={1} is total pages.

PropertyPaneTitle.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra] Append settings to title for the screen reader, {0} is placeholder for webpart title.

PropertyPaneEmptyStateDescription.value: No settings to change for this web part.

PropertyPaneFetchingSettingsDataLabel.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra] Property Pane fetching settings data label.

NoOpOnRefreshPropertyPaneText.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra]Log when it is a no op on refreshPropertyPane. {0} is the web part instance id, which invoked refreshPropertyPane.
NoOpOnRefreshPropertyPaneText.value: refreshPropertyPane is a No Op, because the property pane is currently not attached to the web part {0}.

ApplyButtonAriaDescription.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra]{NeedsReview} Changes made on the property pane will be applied to the web part.
ApplyButtonAriaDescription.value: Changes made on the property pane will be applied to the web part.

ToggleOnText.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra] Label text of toggle control when the toggle is on.

ToggleOffText.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra] Label text of toggle control when the toggle is off.

NoDynamicDataReturnedErrorText.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra]{NeedsReview} Error message for when the entered dynamic resource path does not return any valid data.
NoDynamicDataReturnedErrorText.value: Entered dynamic resource path does not return any dynamic data.

ConnectToDynamicDataSource.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra]{NeedsReview} String displayed on the button to connect to a dynamic data source.

ConnectToDynamicDataSourceDescription.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra]{NeedsReview} Description for screen readers for the connect to source button.
ConnectToDynamicDataSourceDescription.value: Click to connect to a dynamic data source.

DynamicDataSourcesDropdownLabel.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra]{NeedsReview} Label for the dynamic data source dropdown on the DynamicDataWidget. {0} Name of the field.

DynamicDataPropertiesDropdownLabel.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra]{NeedsReview} Label for the properties dropdown on the DynamicDataWidget. {0} is the selected source.

DynamicDataRemoveConnectionText.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra]{NeedsReview} Text for the remove connection button.

DynamicDataApplyButtonText.comment: [Tag:ODSP-SPPPLAT-WebPartInfra]{NeedsReview} Text for the Apply button on the dynamic data widget.
